game.levels

Class AbstractLevel

  • java.lang.Object
    • game.levels.AbstractLevel
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    ColorBarsLvl, FlyingBoxesLvl, SpiralLvl

    public abstract class AbstractLevel
extends java.lang.Object
    Has all the basic principles of any level. It handles the effect of touches and it updates the logic of the objects. All specific level classes can have different layouts and spawn logic.
    Author:
    esa
